Gold View: Sales Analytics (Fact + Dimensions)

This Gold layer view delivers a business-ready dataset by integrating the fact_sales table with dim_customers and dim_products. It enables consistent and reliable analytics across sales, customer, and product domains.

Description

The view enriches transactional sales data with customer and product attributes, creating a unified dataset for reporting and downstream consumption.

Key Features
Combines fact and dimension tables for a denormalized analytical view
Provides customer-level and product-level sales insights
Ensures data consistency across reporting layers
Uses LEFT JOINs to retain all sales records
Data Sources
fact_sales: Core transactional sales data (measures like sales amount, quantity, price)
dim_customers: Customer attributes (e.g., customer name, segment, location)
dim_products: Product attributes (e.g., product name, category, type)

